item.description:
 Elasticsearch Arachne supports storing vertices and edges in Elasticsearch.
Config:
Database: elasticsearch Elasticsearch: URL: &quot;http://localhost:9200&quot; DBName: &quot;arachnedb&quot; Username: &quot;&quot; Password: &quot;&quot;

 MongoDB Arachne supports storing vertices and edges in MongoDB.
Config:
Database: mongodb MongoDB: URL: &quot;localhost:27017&quot; DBName: &quot;arachnedb&quot; Username: &quot;&quot; Password: &quot;&quot;
